channel.title: IS Project Release || custom Grand Exchange || full working Slayer points [508]
channel.description:
hi, i have been working on a 508 just for the fun of it i worked on this about 1-2 weeks ago im just gonna take pictures and name a couple of the features it has as i forgot what most of them are.
[b]features[/b] Custom G.E use the small obelisk to access it(the one you use to renew points in rs). Fully Working Slayer point system not a custom one but real one. Quick Pnpc Transformations VIA quest tab. i forgot the rest just download and check it out
[b]Known Bugs[/b] HP Updating is fucked up.
[b]Server Base[/b] Palidino76.
[b]Download Link[/b] [url=http://up.ht/epXhhz]http://up.ht/epXhhz[/url]
[b]Pictures[/b] [img]http://img43.imageshack.us/img43/2195/090629115104.png[/img] [img]http://img43.imageshack.us/img43/3843/090629115126.png[/img] [img]http://img43.imageshack.us/img43/4162/090629115129.png[/img] [img]http://img43.imageshack.us/img43/7848/090629115158.png[/img] [img]http://img43.imageshack.us/img43/2987/090629115223.png[/img] [img]http://img43.imageshack.us/img43/4339/090629115323.png[/img] [img]http://img43.imageshack.us/img43/5999/090629115354.png[/img] [img]http://img43.imageshack.us/img43/1276/090629115547.png[/img] [img]http://img43.imageshack.us/img43/3346/090629115618.png[/img] [img]http://img43.imageshack.us/img43/1350/090629115648.png[/img] [img]http://img43.imageshack.us/img43/551/090629115803.png[/img] [img]http://img43.imageshack.us/img43/3754/090629115824.png[/img] [img]http://img514.imageshack.us/img514/5760/ewpics.png[/img]
